[Verse 3]

G        C
How I wish,
C                D/F#
how I wish you were here,
D                   Am
We're just two lost souls,
Am                 G
swimming in a fish bowl,
G          D/F#
Year after year,
D                             C
Running over the same old ground,
C               D
What have we found?
D            Am
The same old fears.
 Am              G
Wish you were here.


